      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RIBERY (4) flew the lids last start and led throughout to register his maiden win by 5.5 lengths at this track over 400m (22.70). Can continue the winning form. BRISTOL MOSS (1) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (31.33) at this track behind She's A Jumbo in a Grade 6. Chased the leaders and with a clean run can be prominent. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and three minor placings to her credit. Will give a great sight again. YOU SEE ME (2) trailed the lead and fought on well to be beaten a nose into second (19.86) at Murray Bridge Straight in a Grade 4/5 over 350m. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Leading player again.",
